## Naming Conventions

| Thing | Convention | Example |
|---|---|---|
| Files/folders | kebab-case | `gym-select.tsx`, `crush-signal-button.tsx` |
| Components | PascalCase | `ProfileCard`, `SwipeDeck` |
| Hooks | camelCase with `use` prefix | `useDiscoverFeed`, `useSendCrush` |
| Zustand stores | camelCase with `Store` suffix | `authStore`, `appStore` |
| API hook files | camelCase matching domain | `profiles.ts`, `matches.ts` |
| Zod schemas | camelCase with `Schema` suffix | `profileSchema`, `signupSchema` |
| Types/interfaces | PascalCase | `Profile`, `Match`, `CrushSignal` |
| Constants | SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE | `MAX_PHOTOS`, `CRUSH_SIGNAL_COOLDOWN_HOURS` |
| DB tables | snake_case | `crush_signals`, `user_profiles` |
| Edge functions | kebab-case folders | `handle-crush-signal/` |
| Theme imports | named imports from `@/theme` | `import { colors, gradients } from '@/theme'` |

